message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you today for $14,000. I think you'll find it's a great deal for an item of this quality.
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the quality of the product, but I was hoping to stay within my budget. Would it be possible to negotiate the price down to $11,000?

Thanks for your counteroffer, Bob. I understand your budget constraints, but $14,000 is really the lowest I can go at the moment. This product is worth every penny, and I'm confident you won't be disappointed.
